SAPO,is,a,Portuguese,Internet,service,provider,whose,main,web,site,acts,as,a,web,portal,featuring,a,directory,of,Portuguese,sites,SAPO,Services,provides,a,large,suite,of,web,services,and,applications,to,developers,worldwide,The,PunyURL,service,is,a,URL,shortening,tool,Users,can,submit,a,URL,and,it,returns,two,URLs,one,in,unicode,based,on,RFC,of,PunyCode,and,the,other,with,alphanumeric,characters,in,lowercase,Users,can,also,retrieve,the,original,expanded,URL,for,a,given,short,URL,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON